story :
Hiawanaa is a cook master in the Mohawk Indian tribe or known as the Onondaga tribe. He was fought over by five tribes to get his cooking services. In return each tribal chief presented him with a secret weapon from their tribe and combined it into a great weapon called the Iroquois.
